a momentary force against the pipes wall that was more than seven times greater than the pipes normal operating pressure according to reports issued today by two independent experts commissioned by con edison the pipe itself was found to be in good condition and did not contribute to the event   anger over gas explosion death daily news new york    wilson michael  house exploded just before a check con ed says the new york times retrieved    httpswwwyoutubecomwatchvzaqyzteq  massive con ed transformer explosion blamed for widespread outage cbs october   retrieved october     gabbatt adam how companies used social media during hurricane sandy the guardian february    anderson jared how con edison effectively relied on social media to reach customers during superstorm sandy breaking energy july    sullivan s p state hearing in ramsey will focus on orange  rocklands hurricane sandy response njcom december    santora marc at least  killed as gas explosion hits east harlem new york times march    santora marc rashbaum william k rescue effort in east harlem yields only more victims new york times retrieved  march    httpswwwnytimescomnyregionconedhtmlr  httpwwwcourthousenewscomconedsuesinspectorwhotookbribeshtm  httpwwwnbcnewyorkcomnewslocalnycconedisontopaymillionforbriberyandkickbackshtml  con edison one of americas most admired companies thefreelibrarycom   portero ashley  major us corporations paid more to lobby congress than income taxes – international business times archived from the original on december   retrieved december     latina style announces the  latina style  report latina style    hispanic network magazine announces its spring  early results best of the best lists hispanic network magazine    top  utilities diversity tech retrieved  march   external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to consolidated edison official website con edison inc holding company business data for consolidated edison google finance yahoo finance reuters sec filings v t